Package cp213

Class Reactor

java.lang.Object
cp213.Reactor
public class Reactor
extends java.lang.Object
A simple nuclear reactor simulation. Given a starting temperature and control rods depths, attempt to control the reactor over a period of time.
Version:
2021-07-19
Author:
-- your name here --, David Brown

    • lowerRods

      public void lowerRods()
      Lower the rods by one step. Rods cannot be lowered by more than one step per tick.

    • quit

      public void quit()

      public void raiseRods()
      Raise the rods by one step. Rods cannot be raised by more than one step per tick.

    • tick

      public void tick()
      Increment the simulation tick by one. Update the reactor temperature, power, and status (in that order), and allow the rods to be raised or lowered during this tick.
